<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.1">
<l>āḷum paṇiyu maṭiyēṉaik koṇṭāṉ viṇṭa nicācararai</l>
<l>tōḷun talaiyun tuṇiveytac cuṭuveñ cilaivāyc caranturantāṉ</l>
<l>vēḷuñ cēyu maṉaiyārum vēṟka ṇārum payilvīti</l>
<l>nāḷum viḻavi ṉoliyōvā naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who took me who is humble as his servant whom he rules,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who shot arrows from a fiery, cruel bow,</l>
<l>So heads and arms from the night demons which opposed [him]</l>
<l rend="indent">appeared in pieces,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where the noise of daily festivals</l>
<l rend="indent">never ceases</l>
<l>In the streets where crowd those with spear[-like] eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">and those who are like Kāma and Murukaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
